      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "面对一个庞大又棘手的问题，我们常常无从下手。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "分治的思路是：把大问题一分为二，再各个击破。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "就像整理一副乱牌，先分成两小堆，分别理好，再合到一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "div-1",
      "filename": "divide-div-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/divide-div-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "第一步是分解，把数组从中间切开，得到左右两半。"
