    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "div-2",
      "filename": "divide-div-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/divide-div-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "每一半继续二分，一层层向下，直到只剩单个元素。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "div-3",
      "filename": "divide-div-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/divide-div-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "单个元素天然有序，这就是递归的终点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "conquer",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "conquer-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/conquer-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "每个子问题都用同样的方法处理，这就是递归求解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "conquer",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "conquer-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/conquer-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "递归树的每个分叉，都是一个规模更小的相同问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "mer-1",
      "filename": "merge-mer-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/merge-mer-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "子问题解好后，关键一步是合并：把两个有序小段拼成一个有序大段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "mer-2",
      "filename": "merge-mer-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/merge-mer-2.mp3",
