      "size": 34848,
      "text": "两个指针各指一段头部，每次取较小的放入结果，逐步归并。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "mer-3",
      "filename": "merge-mer-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/xiaoxiao/merge-mer-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "从叶子一路合并回根，整个数组就排好了序。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
